title: Person of Interest - Target confirmed (05x11)
author: POI - Best Of
comment: I think this is my favorite episode because I loved how they brought back the former numbers as a new team. The main characters always thought they were alone then found out The Machine was doing it’s job in more ways than they ever imagined.
I love it how everyone they save came back to save them AHHHH
It was cool until everyone tried to salute and looked like a bunch of actors...
